From ancient barter systems to today’s digital currencies, the way we exchange value has transformed dramatically. Understanding this evolution helps decode the mechanics of our current financial world.

Team Aavishkar brings to you an engaging workshop under Aarohan '25, exploring the journey of money, the inner workings of the monetary system, and the emergence of Bitcoin — a decentralized alternative to traditional currency.

Learn how Bitcoin operates, why it’s considered a game-changer, and uncover the roles of blockchain, transactions, and mining in keeping it secure and functional.

Curious about the future of finance? Be part of this discussion and discover how digital currencies are reshaping the economic landscape.

Are you ready to break barriers, challenge norms, and bring your boldest ideas to life? 

On Spot Hackathon 2025 is your gateway to innovation—a 48-hour adrenaline-fueled coding marathon where your creativity takes center stage! Whether you’re a coding prodigy or a curious beginner, this is your chance to transform ideas into reality and compete with the best.

Unleash your creativity and coding skills at HackOverflow 8.0! As part of Aarohan 2025, this hackathon is your chance to turn bold ideas into reality. Whether you're a coding pro or tech enthusiast, this is where your skills can shine.

HackOverflow 8.0 is a high-energy tech showdown where you'll collaborate, tackle real-world problems, and build game-changing solutions. Win exciting swag from Devfolio and its Season Partners, plus the glory of victory for top teams.
IoT and Cloud Computing in Data Science

Unlock the Future with IoT and Cloud Computing in Data Science

Are you ready to dive into the world of IoT, Cloud Computing, and Data Science with a live project demonstration? This workshop is open to students from all departments, and no prior experience is mandatory. Even if you’re completely new to these technologies, we will guide you step by step from the basics to practical applications.

Key Takeaways:
	•	Completion Certificate & Learning Resources – Strength your CV to secure placement in a promising field.
	•	Live Project Demonstration – Learn from scratch with real-world applications.
	•	Beginner Friendly – No prior knowledge needed, everything starts from the basics.
	•	Build & Implement – Gain industry-relevant skills through practical sessions.
	•	Learn from Industry Experts – Get insights and training from professionals.
	•	Unlock Internship Opportunities – Boost your career with hands-on experience.

Event Details:
Date: 22nd - 23rd March 2025
Time: 9 AM Onwards.
Venue: NAB

Secure your spot now and step into the future of technology. Register today!

Inspiratie: 
The flagship event of the E-Cell, CCA, Inspiratie brings  together successful and renowned personalities from across India to share their inspiring journeys with the bright young minds of NIT Durgapur. Featuring four distinguished speakers, the event serves as a beacon of motivation, offering invaluable insights and experiences. It aims to ignite entrepreneurial spirit, foster innovation, and encourage students to pursue their dreams with passion and resilience.

*Ride the Waves and Rule the Race!*  

Get ready to make a splash at *AAROHAN ’25* with *Aqua Race*, a *thrilling new addition* to the lineup of events! This isn’t just another race - it’s a high-speed *battle of innovation and skill*, where *aqua bots* take on the waves in an electrifying showdown of speed and control.  

It’s not just about being the fastest. It’s about *mastering the currents, navigating the course, and outmaneuvering the competition* to claim victory. A true test of *precision, power, and pure adrenaline*, this race will push your engineering and piloting skills to the limit.  

Think you have what it takes to *dominate the waters and conquer this exciting trial*? The race is on. The tides are wild. *Are you ready to make history?*  

*Dates:* 22nd and 23rd March  
*Time:* 3:00 PM onwards  
*Venue:* Arena  

#AquaRace #AAROHAN25 #TeamAavishkar #ConquerTheWaves #NewChallenge

Team Avishkaar presents Be a Billionaire, a dynamic business simulation event at Aarohan 2025, designed to challenge participants' strategic thinking, decision-making, and entrepreneurial acumen. This event provides a platform to engage in high-stakes negotiations, make calculated investments, and navigate the complexities of the corporate world.

Whether you are an aspiring entrepreneur or a business enthusiast, this competition offers a unique opportunity to test your skills, refine your strategies, and compete with like-minded individuals. The path to success demands foresight, adaptability, and determination-do you have what it takes to rise to the top?

Step into the realm of investigative journalism and detective instincts with Journo Detective, an immersive mystery-solving event at Aarohan 2025, brought to you by Team Avishkaar. This event challenges participants to think critically, analyze evidence, and uncover hidden truths in a thrilling investigative pursuit.

As a detective-journalist, you will navigate through intricate clues, interrogate suspects, and piece together the story behind the mystery. Your skills in deduction, reasoning, and storytelling will determine how far you go in unraveling the case. Do you have what it takes to expose the truth?

Join us for an engaging AI & ML Workshop organized by Remark Skill at NIT Durgapur! This hands-on session will take place on March 22 & 23, from 9:30 AM onwards at the New Academic Building.

Whether you're a beginner or an Al enthusiast, this workshop will introduce you to fundamental Al concepts, machine learning techniques, and practical implementation using Python, TensorFlow, and other essential tools. Gain practical insights through real-world examples and interactive coding exercises.

Don't miss this opportunity to explore the future of Al & ML and build essential skills in these transformative technologies!

We gladly welcome you to Remark Skill's hands-on Ethical Hacking Workshop on March 22 & 23 at the New Academic Building, NIT Durgapur. This session covers network security, penetration testing, vulnerability assessment, and ethical hacking techniques.

Gain practical experience through real-world simulations, learn to secure systems, detect threats, and protect data. Enhance your cybersecurity skills and prepare for a career in this high-demand field.

Register now to earn a certificate of completion and engage with industry experts on real-world challenges.

*RoboLiga at Aarohan ‘25 – The Ultimate Bot Soccer Battle!*

Get ready for *RoboLiga*, where robotics meets the thrill of soccer in an intense battle of skill and strategy! Hosted by *Team AAVISHKAR*, this offline adaptation of *Rocket League* pits participants against each other in a fast-paced, goal-scoring showdown.  

This isn’t just about controlling a robot—it’s about precision, quick reflexes, and outplaying your opponent in a test of technical mastery. Will you rise to the occasion and claim victory?  

*Rules & Gameplay*
1. *On-Spot Registration:* Individual participation only.  
2. *1v1 Matches:* Two participants compete against each other.  
3. *Objective:* Control your bot to score the first goal.  
4. *Match Format:* The first player to score wins the round.   
5. *Fair Play:* No external interference or intentional bot damage.  
6. *Tiebreaker:* If no goal is scored within the time limit, a sudden-death round will decide the winner.

*Speedcubing at Aarohan 2025 – Twist, Turn, and Triumph!*
